Whimsicott (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0546: Cottonee
Pokémon
#0548: Petilil →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Whimsicott (TCG Pocket).

Whimsicott has been featured on 16 different cards since it debuted in the Emerging Powers expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Whimsicott cards are normally Grass-type or Psychic-type Stage 1 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Whimsicott

Whimsicott
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
